name: KheyouMix [1b8b712d80]
description:
Done for the JVC community, mix of Bastard v4 and AbyssOrangeMix with the MBW extention.

Just a "starter pack" model, don't really overthink it.

Best vae to use is "vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.vae.pt" uploaded with the model.

Parameters:

  • Steps: 10 minimum.

  • Size : 512x512 minimum.

  • Highres x2, ~30 step is absolutely beautiful, ~0.65 denoising strengh

  • Best Method : Eular A, DPM ++ 2M Karras
